&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/LAS-VEGAS-TAO-BEACH-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8329&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/LAS-VEGAS-TAO-BEACH-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;LAS VEGAS- TAO BEACH- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;148&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Since opening in September 2005, this design-driven dining and entertainment complex in The Venetian has proven to be a hot spot like its sister venue in New York City. The multi-faceted and multi-story &ldquo;Asian City&rdquo; houses a restaurant, banquet facilities, lounge, nightclub and beach in 60,000 square-feet. Located on top of the venue is TAO Beach, which is open daily during pool season and brings all of the aspects of the restaurant and club to an incredible daytime party.&nbsp;Dress code: Swimwear casual.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please send an email to&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:lifestyle@taogroup.com&quot;&gt;lifestylelv@taogroup.com&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp; &lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;to make your reservation. Provide&nbsp;your name, date you would like to attend, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address. You will be provided with all details and instructions for general admission or table/bottle service reservation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 21 &amp;amp; Over. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit is applicable for up to 2 guests in total.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dress code will be strictly enforced. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access is granted only with reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Late arrivals past midnight will be required to pay any required cover charges, despite having a reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Nightclub/Lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs many incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

